         http://placehold.it 
      .row-fluid.section1
        .span5.offset1.asset
          a(href='hang10-canvas-jpg_med.jpg', target='_blank')
            img.img-polaroid(src='/images/hang10-canvas-jpg_sm.jpg')
        .span5.copy
          p
            | On the left you see the
            a(href='http://leancanvas.com/blog/why-lean-canvas-vs-business-model-canvas') Lean Canvas
            | that fleshes out the idea for Hang10.app.
          p
            | The
            b Unique Value Proposition
            | (UVP) is that the users of this app are focused on just hanging out with friends, not planning future events or reminiscing of the past.
          p
            | Why is that important? Because when you just want to hang out, all other stuff is noise. Are your friends down for a couple of brewskis or not? Not later, not tomorrow, but now! When you have two hours and not a minute more, idle chatter of how "it would be nice to meet up some day" just don't cut it!
          p
            b So next time it's time to hang – use Hang10!
